```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    %% Enterprise Data Lakehouse - ETL Pipeline Flow
    %% Detailed sequence diagram showing extraction to gold aggregation

    participant SourceDB as Source Systems<br/>(RDS, DynamoDB, APIs)
    participant EventBridge as Amazon EventBridge<br/>Scheduler
    participant StepFunctions as Step Functions<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Lambda as Lambda Functions<br/>Extractors
    participant DMS as AWS DMS<br/>CDC Service
    participant RawZone as S3 Raw Zone<br/>Landing
    participant GlueCrawler as Glue Crawler<br/>Metadata
    participant GlueCatalog as Glue Data Catalog<br/>Registry
    participant GlueJob as Glue ETL Jobs<br/>Transformation
    participant DataQuality as Glue Data Quality<br/>Validation
    participant BronzeZone as S3 Bronze Zone<br/>Validated
    participant EMRCluster as EMR Spark Cluster<br/>Processing
    participant SilverZone as S3 Silver Zone<br/>Delta Lake
    participant AthenaSQL as Amazon Athena<br/>SQL Engine
    participant GoldZone as S3 Gold Zone<br/>Aggregates
    participant SNS as Amazon SNS<br/>Notifications
    participant CloudWatch as CloudWatch<br/>Monitoring
    participant ErrorQueue as DLQ<br/>Dead Letter Queue

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 1: EXTRACTION
    %% ========================================

    Note over SourceDB,ErrorQueue: Phase 1: Data Extraction (Daily 2:00 AM UTC)

    EventBridge->>StepFunctions: Trigger daily ETL workflow<br/>Schedule: cron(0 2 * * ? *)
    activate StepFunctions

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Log workflow start<br/>Execution ID: exec-20260310-001
    CloudWatch-->>StepFunctions: Logged

    par Full Extract Path
        StepFunctions->>Lambda: Extract RDS full dump<br/>Table: customers
        activate Lambda
        Lambda->>SourceDB: SELECT * FROM customers<br/>WHERE updated_at >= ?
        SourceDB-->>Lambda: 100K rows returned

        Lambda->>Lambda: Validate row count<br/>Check: count > 0
        Lambda->>Lambda: Calculate checksum<br/>MD5 hash

        Lambda->>RawZone: Write to S3<br/>s3://raw/rds/customers/<br/>date=2026-03-10/data.json
        RawZone-->>Lambda: Upload complete<br/>Size: 50 MB

        Lambda->>CloudWatch: Log extraction metrics<br/>Rows: 100K, Duration: 45s
        deactivate Lambda

    and CDC Path
        StepFunctions->>DMS: Check CDC changes<br/>Table: orders
        activate DMS
        DMS->>SourceDB: Read binlog/WAL<br/>Since last checkpoint
        SourceDB-->>DMS: 5K change records

        DMS->>DMS: Parse CDC events<br/>INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE
        DMS->>DMS: Add metadata<br/>timestamp, operation

        DMS->>RawZone: Write CDC log<br/>s3://raw/cdc/orders/<br/>date=2026-03-10/changes.json
        RawZone-->>DMS: Upload complete<br/>Size: 2 MB
        deactivate DMS

    and API Extract Path
        StepFunctions->>Lambda: Extract Salesforce API<br/>Object: Account
        activate Lambda
        Lambda->>SourceDB: GET /services/data/v56.0/<br/>query?q=SELECT...
        SourceDB-->>Lambda: API response: 200<br/>10K records

        Lambda->>Lambda: Handle pagination<br/>Next page token
        Lambda->>SourceDB: GET next page
        SourceDB-->>Lambda: 10K more records

        Lambda->>Lambda: Rate limit check<br/>Wait if needed

        Lambda->>RawZone: Write to S3<br/>s3://raw/api/salesforce/<br/>date=2026-03-10/accounts.json
        RawZone-->>Lambda: Upload complete
        deactivate Lambda
    end

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Extraction phase complete<br/>Duration: 2 minutes

    %% Error handling for extraction
    alt Extraction Error
        Lambda->>ErrorQueue: Send failed extraction<br/>Error: Connection timeout
        ErrorQueue->>SNS: Publish alert<br/>Priority: P1
        SNS->>CloudWatch: Alert sent to on-call
    end

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 2: RAW TO BRONZE TRANSFORMATION
    %% ========================================

    Note over RawZone,ErrorQueue: Phase 2: Bronze Transformation (Validation & Standardization)

    StepFunctions->>GlueCrawler: Crawl raw zone<br/>Update catalog
    activate GlueCrawler
    GlueCrawler->>RawZone: Scan new files<br/>Pattern: date=2026-03-10/*
    RawZone-->>GlueCrawler: Files discovered: 15

    GlueCrawler->>GlueCrawler: Infer schemas<br/>Sample 2 MB per file
    GlueCrawler->>GlueCatalog: Update tables<br/>Create partitions
    GlueCatalog-->>GlueCrawler: Catalog updated
    deactivate GlueCrawler

    StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Start Bronze transformation<br/>Job: raw_to_bronze_customers
    activate GlueJob

    GlueJob->>GlueCatalog: Read table metadata<br/>Table: raw.customers
    GlueCatalog-->>GlueJob: Schema returned

    GlueJob->>RawZone: Read raw data<br/>Partition: date=2026-03-10
    RawZone-->>GlueJob: 100K rows loaded

    GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 1: Parse JSON<br/>Handle nested structures
    GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 2: Flatten schema<br/>Normalize columns
    GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 3: Data type casting<br/>String -> Int/Date/etc

    GlueJob->>DataQuality: Run quality rules<br/>Ruleset: bronze_customers
    activate DataQuality

    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule 1: Null check<br/>customer_id NOT NULL
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule 2: Format check<br/>email MATCHES regex
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule 3: Range check<br/>created_at <= NOW()
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule 4: Uniqueness<br/>customer_id unique

    DataQuality-->>GlueJob: Quality score: 96.5%<br/>Failed: 3,500 rows
    deactivate DataQuality

    alt Quality Score < 95%
        GlueJob->>ErrorQueue: Quality failure<br/>Score below threshold
        ErrorQueue->>SNS: Alert data team<br/>Priority: P2
        GlueJob->>StepFunctions: Fail job
        StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Job failed - quality
    else Quality Score >= 95%
        GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 4: Remove invalid rows<br/>Write to quarantine
        GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 5: Add metadata<br/>processing_time, job_id
        GlueJob->>GlueJob: Step 6: Partition data<br/>By year/month/day

        GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Write Parquet files<br/>s3://bronze/customers/<br/>year=2026/month=03/day=10/
        BronzeZone-->>GlueJob: Write complete<br/>96,500 rows, 18 MB

        GlueJob->>GlueCatalog: Update statistics<br/>Row count, file size
        GlueCatalog-->>GlueJob: Stats updated

        GlueJob->>CloudWatch: Log job metrics<br/>Success, 96.5% quality
        deactivate GlueJob
    end

    %% Parallel Bronze jobs
    par Other Bronze Jobs
        StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Transform orders table
        activate GlueJob
        Note right of GlueJob: Similar steps:<br/>Parse, validate,<br/>cast types,<br/>quality check,<br/>write Parquet
        GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Write orders Bronze
        deactivate GlueJob

    and Products Bronze
        StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Transform products table
        activate GlueJob
        GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Write products Bronze
        deactivate GlueJob

    and Events Bronze
        StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Transform clickstream
        activate GlueJob
        GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Write events Bronze
        deactivate GlueJob
    end

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Bronze phase complete<br/>Duration: 15 minutes

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 3: BRONZE TO SILVER TRANSFORMATION
    %% ========================================

    Note over BronzeZone,ErrorQueue: Phase 3: Silver Transformation (Business Logic & SCD)

    StepFunctions->>EMRCluster: Submit Spark job<br/>Job: bronze_to_silver_dim_customer
    activate EMRCluster

    EMRCluster->>GlueCatalog: Read table schema<br/>Table: bronze.customers
    GlueCatalog-->>EMRCluster: Schema metadata

    EMRCluster->>BronzeZone: Read Bronze data<br/>Spark DataFrame
    BronzeZone-->>EMRCluster: 96,500 rows loaded

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 1: Deduplication<br/>PARTITION BY customer_id<br/>ORDER BY updated_at DESC

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: Read existing Silver<br/>Table: dim_customer<br/>Delta Lake
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: Current dimension: 950K rows

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 2: SCD Type 2 logic<br/>Compare new vs existing

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Identify changes:<br/>- New customers: 2,500<br/>- Updated customers: 5,000<br/>- No change: 89,000

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 3: Close expired records<br/>SET effective_to = NOW()<br/>SET is_current = false

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 4: Insert new versions<br/>SET effective_from = NOW()<br/>SET effective_to = '9999-12-31'<br/>SET is_current = true

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 5: Data enrichment<br/>- Geocode addresses<br/>- Calculate age<br/>- Derive segments

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 6: Business rules<br/>- Email validation<br/>- Phone formatting<br/>- Name standardization

    EMRCluster->>DataQuality: Validate Silver quality<br/>Ruleset: silver_dim_customer
    activate DataQuality

    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule: Referential integrity<br/>Check foreign keys
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule: No duplicates<br/>current records only
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Rule: Complete history<br/>No gaps in effective dates

    DataQuality-->>EMRCluster: Quality score: 99.2%
    deactivate DataQuality

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: MERGE into Delta table<br/>ACID transaction
    activate SilverZone
    SilverZone->>SilverZone: Start transaction
    SilverZone->>SilverZone: Update expired records
    SilverZone->>SilverZone: Insert new records
    SilverZone->>SilverZone: Commit transaction
    SilverZone->>SilverZone: Optimize table<br/>Compaction + Z-ordering
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: Merge complete<br/>Total rows: 957,500
    deactivate SilverZone

    EMRCluster->>GlueCatalog: Update table stats<br/>Latest partition info
    GlueCatalog-->>EMRCluster: Updated

    EMRCluster->>CloudWatch: Log Spark metrics<br/>Shuffle: 2.5 GB<br/>Duration: 8 minutes
    deactivate EMRCluster

    %% Silver Fact Table Processing
    StepFunctions->>EMRCluster: Submit fact_sales job
    activate EMRCluster

    EMRCluster->>BronzeZone: Read orders Bronze
    BronzeZone-->>EMRCluster: Orders loaded

    EMRCluster->>BronzeZone: Read order_items Bronze
    BronzeZone-->>EMRCluster: Line items loaded

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: Read dim_customer<br/>For joins
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: Dimension loaded

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: Read dim_product<br/>For joins
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: Dimension loaded

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: Read dim_date<br/>For joins
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: Dimension loaded

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 1: Join operations<br/>orders <- order_items<br/>LEFT JOIN dimensions

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 2: Calculate measures<br/>- Line total<br/>- Discounts<br/>- Tax amounts<br/>- Profit margins

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 3: Handle late arrivals<br/>Check processing_date<br/>vs order_date

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 4: Deduplication<br/>Remove duplicate orders

    EMRCluster->>DataQuality: Validate fact table<br/>Referential integrity
    activate DataQuality
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Check all FKs exist<br/>in dimensions
    DataQuality->>DataQuality: Check measure ranges<br/>Amount > 0, Qty > 0
    DataQuality-->>EMRCluster: Quality: 99.8%
    deactivate DataQuality

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: APPEND to fact_sales<br/>Delta Lake
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: 45,000 rows appended

    EMRCluster->>CloudWatch: Fact job complete<br/>Duration: 12 minutes
    deactivate EMRCluster

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Silver phase complete<br/>Duration: 25 minutes

    alt Silver Phase Error
        EMRCluster->>ErrorQueue: Job failure<br/>Error: OOM exception
        ErrorQueue->>SNS: Alert engineers<br/>Priority: P1
        SNS->>CloudWatch: On-call notified
        StepFunctions->>StepFunctions: Retry with more memory<br/>Max retries: 3
    end

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 4: SILVER TO GOLD AGGREGATION
    %% ========================================

    Note over SilverZone,ErrorQueue: Phase 4: Gold Aggregation (Business Metrics)

    StepFunctions->>AthenaSQL: Execute aggregation query<br/>CTAS: gold_sales_analytics
    activate AthenaSQL

    AthenaSQL->>GlueCatalog: Read Silver schemas<br/>fact_sales + dimensions
    GlueCatalog-->>AthenaSQL: Schemas returned

    AthenaSQL->>SilverZone: Scan Silver data<br/>Predicates pushed down
    SilverZone-->>AthenaSQL: Optimized read<br/>Only required columns

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Step 1: Daily aggregation<br/>GROUP BY date, customer, product<br/>SUM(revenue, profit, units)

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Step 2: Calculate KPIs<br/>- Profit margin %<br/>- Growth rate YoY<br/>- Running totals<br/>- Moving averages

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Step 3: Monthly rollup<br/>Aggregate daily to monthly

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Step 4: YTD calculations<br/>Running YTD sums

    AthenaSQL->>GoldZone: Write aggregated data<br/>CREATE TABLE AS SELECT<br/>Format: Delta Lake
    GoldZone-->>AthenaSQL: Table created<br/>5,000 aggregated rows

    AthenaSQL->>GlueCatalog: Register Gold table<br/>Update partitions
    GlueCatalog-->>AthenaSQL: Registered

    AthenaSQL->>CloudWatch: Log query metrics<br/>Data scanned: 500 MB<br/>Duration: 45 seconds
    deactivate AthenaSQL

    %% Customer 360 Gold Table
    StepFunctions->>EMRCluster: Build Customer 360<br/>Wide table denormalized
    activate EMRCluster

    EMRCluster->>SilverZone: Read multiple Silver tables<br/>- dim_customer<br/>- fact_sales<br/>- fact_web_sessions<br/>- fact_support_tickets
    SilverZone-->>EMRCluster: All loaded

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 1: Customer aggregates<br/>COUNT orders, SUM revenue<br/>AVG order value, etc

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 2: RFM metrics<br/>Recency, Frequency, Monetary

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 3: Segmentation<br/>ML-based clustering<br/>High/Medium/Low value

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 4: Lifetime value<br/>CLV calculation<br/>Predictive LTV

    EMRCluster->>EMRCluster: Step 5: Flatten to wide table<br/>200+ columns per customer

    EMRCluster->>GoldZone: Write Customer 360<br/>Delta Lake MERGE
    GoldZone-->>EMRCluster: Complete: 950K customers

    deactivate EMRCluster

    %% Executive KPI Dashboard
    StepFunctions->>AthenaSQL: Build Executive KPIs<br/>Highest aggregation
    activate AthenaSQL

    AthenaSQL->>GoldZone: Read multiple Gold marts<br/>- Sales analytics<br/>- Financial metrics<br/>- Marketing performance
    GoldZone-->>AthenaSQL: Data loaded

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Calculate top-level KPIs<br/>- Total revenue<br/>- YoY growth<br/>- Customer count<br/>- Churn rate<br/>- Net profit margin

    AthenaSQL->>AthenaSQL: Compare to targets<br/>Variance analysis<br/>Green/Yellow/Red status

    AthenaSQL->>GoldZone: Write KPI dashboard table<br/>Highly summarized
    GoldZone-->>AthenaSQL: 50 KPI rows written

    deactivate AthenaSQL

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Gold phase complete<br/>Duration: 10 minutes

    %% ========================================
    %% PHASE 5: POST-PROCESSING
    %% ========================================

    Note over StepFunctions,ErrorQueue: Phase 5: Post-Processing & Notifications

    StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Run data quality report<br/>Aggregated metrics
    activate GlueJob

    GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Query row counts<br/>Quality scores
    BronzeZone-->>GlueJob: Bronze metrics

    GlueJob->>SilverZone: Query row counts<br/>Quality scores
    SilverZone-->>GlueJob: Silver metrics

    GlueJob->>GoldZone: Query row counts<br/>Freshness timestamps
    GoldZone-->>GlueJob: Gold metrics

    GlueJob->>GlueJob: Generate quality report<br/>Calculate scores<br/>Identify issues

    GlueJob->>CloudWatch: Publish DQ metrics<br/>Custom metrics
    CloudWatch-->>GlueJob: Metrics published

    deactivate GlueJob

    StepFunctions->>StepFunctions: Check SLA compliance<br/>Target: 3 hours end-to-end

    alt SLA Met
        StepFunctions->>SNS: Success notification<br/>All zones updated<br/>Quality: 98.5%<br/>Duration: 52 minutes
        SNS->>CloudWatch: Notification sent

    else SLA Missed
        StepFunctions->>SNS: SLA breach alert<br/>Duration: 190 minutes<br/>Target: 180 minutes
        SNS->>CloudWatch: Alert escalated
    end

    StepFunctions->>CloudWatch: Workflow complete<br/>Status: SUCCESS<br/>Total duration: 52 minutes<br/>Records processed: 500K

    deactivate StepFunctions

    %% ========================================
    %% ERROR HANDLING FLOW
    %% ========================================

    Note over ErrorQueue,CloudWatch: Error Handling & Recovery

    opt Error Recovery Path
        ErrorQueue->>Lambda: Process DLQ messages<br/>Retry with backoff
        activate Lambda

        Lambda->>Lambda: Analyze error type<br/>Transient vs Permanent

        alt Transient Error
            Lambda->>StepFunctions: Retry failed step<br/>Attempt: 2/3
            StepFunctions->>GlueJob: Re-run job
            GlueJob->>BronzeZone: Second attempt
            BronzeZone-->>GlueJob: Success

        else Permanent Error
            Lambda->>SNS: Manual intervention needed<br/>Error: Schema mismatch<br/>Priority: P0
            SNS->>CloudWatch: Engineering team alerted
        end

        deactivate Lambda
    end

    %% Monitoring Dashboard
    Note over CloudWatch: All metrics visualized in CloudWatch Dashboard<br/>Real-time monitoring + alerting
```
